<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">SCP-027-J？</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/div]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/div]]</span><br />
<strong>结果：</strong></p>
<div class="scp-image-block" style="width:200px; float: right;">
