</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div style="border: black 1px solid; margin-left: 10%; margin-right: 10%; background:lightgray;">
<ul>
<li>评分选择器：<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-10" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-10')">10</a></sup>
